flowchart TD
    A([User Preferences\n
    genre · mood · energy · valence
    acousticness · danceability · bpm]) --> B

    B[Load songs.csv\n20 songs] --> C

    C{For each song...} --> D

    D[Score the song\n\n+ 4.0 genre match\n+ 2.0 mood match\n+ 3.0 × energy sim\n+ 2.0 × valence sim\n+ 1.5 × acousticness sim\n+ 1.0 × danceability sim\n+ 0.5 × bpm sim] --> E

    E[Append score\nto results list] --> F{More songs?}

    F -- Yes --> C
    F -- No --> G

    G[Sort results\nby score descending] --> H

    H([Top K Recommendations\nTitle · Artist · Score])
